issue_text:
Minimist <=1.2.5 is vulnerable to Prototype Pollution via file index.js, function setKey() (lines 69-95).


**Is fix available?** Yes, this issue was fixed in the following versions: 0.2.4, 1.2.6

This affects the package glob-parent before 5.1.2. The enclosure regex used to check for strings ending in enclosure containing path separator. Please upgrade to 5.1.2. https://github.com/advisories/GHSA-ww39-953v-wcq6


**Is fix available?** Yes, this issue was fixed in version 5.1.2
